425
00:18:54,030 --> 00:18:57,300
Suppose we really do
have a maximum m plus.

426
00:18:57,300 --> 00:19:01,190
That means that if I try to
raise the state Ylm plus,

427
00:19:01,190 --> 00:19:05,420
