428
00:19:05,420 --> 00:19:07,120
So suppose this is true.

429
00:19:07,120 --> 00:19:10,210
In that case, in particular
here's the nice trick,

430
00:19:10,210 --> 00:19:12,830
L plus Ylm, if we
take its magnitude,

